{"TopicId":48260,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Possibly the worst decision the devs have ever made so far.","CreatedByName":"BeefTenderloin","CreatedById":25612,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-13T19:34:37Z","PageNum":3,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dooz","CreatedById":74263,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T10:21:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI don\u0027t understand why people hate it its just a font\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AntonioAJC","CreatedById":16486,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T10:36:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022littlebattler\u0022 data-cite=\u0022littlebattler\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI... don\u0027t see a problem with using comic sans there\u003Cp\u003E1. It\u0027s not overused\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2. It\u0027s not everywhere\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E3. You only get to see it when it\u0027s opened.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EStop font discrimination. It\u0027s like racism, only worst.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E^ This. I do not know what\u0027s the problem. I do not know why people hate the font. But, guess what? IT DOESN\u0027T MATTER! IT\u0027S A FONT! Seriously, deal with it. I can read these letters just fine.... Unless it\u0027s the symbols font. Can\u0027t read that.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T11:04:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brotoro\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Brotoro\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI\u0027m always surprised that kerbals apparently write in English, but speak in backward Spanish. How does that work?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWould you rather see all text in backward Spanish?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sidew","CreatedById":57794,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T11:30:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://comicsanscriminal.com/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://comicsanscriminal.com/\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"manskal","CreatedById":73159,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T11:41:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027;\u0022\u003EComic Sans\u003C/span\u003E is not inherently evil. It is just misused and misunderstood. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt is a comic-style font but it totally looks out of place in a comic book. Seriously. Have you ever seen a comic\u0027s dialogue written \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027;\u0022\u003Eas such?\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-10-14T11:42:27Z\u0022 title=\u002210/14/2013 11:42  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 14, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by manskal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EHighlighted the given sample of text.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuperWeegee4000","CreatedById":71621,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T13:44:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dooz\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Dooz\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI don\u0027t understand why people hate it its just a font\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis right here.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kasuha","CreatedById":81781,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T14:29:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EComic sans is font used by scientists. There\u0027s no doubt about it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cdn3.sbnation.com/entry_photo_images/4560887/CERN_comic_sans_higgs_large_verge_medium_landscape.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022CERN_comic_sans_higgs_large_verge_medium_landscape.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWith that said, if all you are complaining about is that short warning on the science machine then I think its use there given the context is completely appropriate.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-10-14T14:35:03Z\u0022 title=\u002210/14/2013 02:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 14, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Kasuha\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lanfranc","CreatedById":67288,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T15:00:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022luchelibre\u0022 data-cite=\u0022luchelibre\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EPfft... You are all godless heathens. Leaving behind the serif had led you all down the broad path to destruction.\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Times New Roman\u0027;\u0022\u003ETimes New Roman and a three-piece tuxedo are for the enlightened man.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETimes New Roman, oh please. The true connoisseur obviously uses Didot. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceSphereOfDeath","CreatedById":69754,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T15:11:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Century Gothic\u0027;\u0022\u003ECentury Gothic FTW!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pipcard","CreatedById":2541,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T15:11:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027comic sans ms\u0027;\u0022\u003EI used to love Comic Sans a lot. At one time, I even replaced every font on my computer with it.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027century gothic\u0027;\u0022\u003EBut now I\u0027m into Century Gothic. Very modern.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Technical Ben","CreatedById":10512,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T15:13:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWould you rather see all text in backward Spanish?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs long as it\u0027s not Papyrus...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EvilotionCR2","CreatedById":27754,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T15:17:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027comic sans ms\u0027;\u0022\u003EWhy people hate comic sans?\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuperWeegee4000","CreatedById":71621,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T16:26:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Arial Black\u0027;\u0022\u003EArial Black is fun to use.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Javster","CreatedById":74613,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T17:01:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs this seriously a thread about \u003Cstrong\u003Efonts???\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T17:02:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Javster\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Javster\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIs this seriously a thread about \u003Cstrong\u003Efonts???\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo. It\u0027s far from serious.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jue623","CreatedById":85317,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T17:13:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Console\u0027;\u0022\u003ELucida Console is one of my favourites, just because it has zombies in it. \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Console\u0027;\u0022\u003Ei\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Beachernaut","CreatedById":69994,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T17:27:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EForget about a bit of font. There are some rocket parts that are gray when they should really be slate. CMON Squad!!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andrew Hansen","CreatedById":82311,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T17:27:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYeah, I am flabbergasted that so many people would write a whole seven pages about fonts! Personally, I like the theory that the guy who started this thread was joking. And I like comic sans anyway. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"oggylt","CreatedById":57214,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T18:02:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice detail you saw there! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E I would never had noticed that by myself \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSK","CreatedById":61025,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T18:12:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wolfedg\u0022 data-cite=\u0022wolfedg\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EFirst it was grammar nazis, now people are whining about a font that doesn\u0027t even look that bad. If it was wingdings then I (might) understand.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EActually, Kerbals read and write in Wingdings. However, Squad have thoughtfully translated them into something more accessible to Terrans \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Motokid600","CreatedById":66349,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T19:02:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI can dig it. Can you dig it?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Herbert McCheese-Wang","CreatedById":68660,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T19:06:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENOOOOOOOOOO! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKill it before it lays eggs!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nexustrimean","CreatedById":33308,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T19:39:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECould be worse. it could have been papyrus.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Holo","CreatedById":39606,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T20:06:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027;\u0022\u003EDon\u0027t you get it? The kerbals use comic sans ms to \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027;\u0022\u003Eemphasise how poor they are at font choice!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SuperWeegee4000","CreatedById":71621,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-10-14T20:47:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Holo\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Holo\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027;\u0022\u003EDon\u0027t you get it? The kerbals use comic sans ms to \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027;\u0022\u003Eemphasise how poor they are at font choice!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESeriously, why does everyone hate Comic Sans? It\u0027s a font.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}